<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Panel Order Taker</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/font-awesome@4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            hotel: { dark: '#0F2B48', primary: '#2D5B7C', light: '#E8F0F5', accent: '#F2994A', success: '#27AE60', danger: '#E74C3C', neutral: '#F8FAFC' }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-hotel-neutral min-h-screen">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-3 py-4 max-w-3xl">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md mb-5 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="bg-hotel-dark text-white p-4 flex justify-between items-center">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-lg font-bold">Panel Order Taker</h1>
          <p class="text-sm">Selamat datang, <%= user.nama %></p>
        </div>
        <a href="/logout" class="bg-red-500 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm"><i class="fa fa-sign-out"></i> Keluar</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 text-center">
      <i class="fa fa-headphones text-5xl text-hotel-primary mb-4"></i>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-hotel-dark mb-2">Modul Pesanan & Koordinasi</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Halaman ini digunakan untuk mencatat permintaan tamu dan mengoordinasikan kebutuhan kebersihan kamar.</p>
      <div class="bg-hotel-light p-4 rounded-md text-left text-sm text-gray-700">
        <p class="font-medium mb-2">Informasi:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>Semua permintaan tamu akan diteruskan ke tim Room Attendant</li>
          <li>Status kamar dapat dipantau secara real-time</li>
          <li>Laporan dapat dilihat oleh Supervisor</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
